    "IFX VIP PLATINUM"
  ];
  var accountsSubTitle = [
    "The world of trading starts with </br>IFX Lite",
    "Passionate about trading? </br>IFX Silver is for you",
    "Go for gold! The Pro standard",
    "Premium choice for Institutional </br>Traders and Wealthy Individuals"
  ];
  var accountsText = [
    "Open a trading account with as little as US$100 and qualify for access to the IFX Academy.",
    "Passionate about trading? This account is the retailer’s first choice because it requires an opening deposit of only US$500 with extremely flexible position sizing and it gives you access to the IFX Academy.",
