    "Our premium trading package, the IFX VIP Platinum account is designed especially for trading high rollers who want RAW, pure ECN spreads from our top tier 1 liquidity providers. Your minimum deposit of US$20,000 secures your own personal account manager."
  ];
  var accountsPrice = [
    "$100",
